Context("Numeric"); 

$a = random(2, 7, 1);
$b = random(4, 10, 1);    
$c = random(2, 9, 1);
$ans = 2*$a+$c-2*$b;
     
BEGIN_PGML
Here is a definition: [`f(a, b) = 2a-b`].    

Solve for [`x`]: [`f([$a], x) = f([$b], [$c]). \hspace{1em} x = `] [____]{Compute("$ans")}

END_PGML

